                <h2>Netwrk’s Copyright Policy</h2>
                <h3>What types of copyright complaints does Netwrk respond to?</h3>
                <p>Netwrk responds to copyright complaints submitted under the Digital Millennium Copyright Act (“DMCA”). Section 512 of the DMCA outlines the statutory requirements necessary for formally reporting copyright infringement, as well as providing instructions on how an affected party can appeal a removal by submitting a compliant counter-notice.</p>
