                <p>If you are unsure whether you hold rights to a particular work, please consult an attorney or another adviser as Netwrk cannot provide legal advice. There are plenty of resources to learn more about copyright law including  http://copyright.gov, https://lumendatabase.org/, and http://www.eff.org/issues/bloggers/legal/liability/IP, to name a few.</p>

